textbox "normal text" xleft 1.735 ytop 2.195 text "These yellow molecules represent$n$nitrogen molecules, which have $n$only a weak affinity for each$n$other but a stronger attraction to $n$the nickel.$n$(We have not attempted to use accurate$n$interaction parameters so what$n$we call the molecules is a bit arbitrary.$n$We are looking only at general behaviour.)" id 3;
